nodes.text: Bodie Taylor (born 1976, New Zealand) is the actor who portrayed the clones of Jango Fett when they were age-equivalent to his twenties during Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones. He also portrayed a clone pilot in Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith.
